name: Circular Papercut Greetings Card with Message
description: This card features an circular papercut design, mounted on a complimentary background colour and affixed to cream card with a split-pin, allowing it to turn. The card can be personalised with any message up to about 30 characters (including spaces), and can be decorated in any way you choose. Just send me a message using the 'Contact' option to the right, and I will list a special card reserved for you to buy in the drop-down box below. Alternatively, choose one of the options already listed to order a card ready-made. Click here to view pictures of the other options. Each card is sent in a good-quality envelope and backed by a piece of thick cardboard - they are quite fragile! Please allow 5 days for delivery.

name: Circular Papercut Greetings Card without Message
description:
This card features an circular papercut design, mounted on a complimentary background colour and affixed to cream card with a split-pin, allowing it to turn. The card can be personalised with any design you choose. I'm happy to help with the design - just send me a message using the 'Contact' option to the right, telling me the occasion and recipient, and we can decide on a card. Once you're happy with the card, I will list a special card reserved for you to buy in the drop-down box below. Alternatively, choose one of the options already listed to order a card ready-made.

Each card is sent in a good-quality envelope and backed by a piece of thick cardboard - they are quite fragile! Please allow 7 days for delivery.
